               <name xml:id="tag39" type="place">
          Lyons:
        </name>
            </rs>
            <lb/>
where he was confined not because He<lb/>
professed Magic but because He had<lb/>
violently abused <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
