And the history of this Institution is secret<lb/>
as obscure as that of the kindred Sect of<lb/>
the modern illuminees.-<lb/>
It would be of little use and foreign<lb/>
to the objects of these lectures to enter upon<lb/>
an examination of all the writings published<lb/>
on Alchemy in different parts of Europe<lb/>
by Valentine by Fludd by <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
