And a true and enlightened <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">science</hi>
            <lb/>
arose by degree and amidst clouds<lb/>
and obscurity from the <add xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">furnaces</add>
