               <name xml:id="tag59" type="person">
          Agricola
        </name>
            </rs> was the <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">first person</hi>
            <lb/>
who published <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">on</del> practical mineralogy<lb/>
