                rend="underline">the last</hi> created<lb/>
and most perfect <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">of beings</hi>
            <lb/>
            <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
