                type="person">
               <name xml:id="tag87" type="person">
          Leibnitz
        </name>
            </rs> supposes that there may have<lb/>
been two causes for the deluge:-<lb/>
The elevation of Land in the former bed<lb/>
of the Ocean in consequence of explosions<lb/>
from the central ignited mass: and<lb/>
            <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
