Such is the doctrine of the <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                xml:id="ttag90"
                ref="#otherwork_318"
                type="otherwork">
               <bibl xml:id="tag90">
            Protogaea
        </bibl>
            </rs>
            <lb/>
as found in the excellent edition of the<lb/>
